CustomField.description: This option allows linking a queue with a click-to-dial number. If a valid configuration exists, a button will appear on the right side in the queues list for that particular queue to execute the click-to-dial.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This option allows linking a queue with a click-to-dial number. If a valid configuration exists, a button will appear on the right side in the queues list for that particular queue to execute the click-to-dial.
CustomField.label: Click-to-Dial Queue
